---
title: Stovetop Cajun Spiced Double Prawn Risotto with Crispy Onions
description: Making a risotto on the hob or stove is simpler than you think, with only three stirs needed to absorb the stock and flavours. This Stovetop Cajun Spiced Prawn Risotto uses Cajun spice mix for a punchy flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R28_W10_UK_R3417-50_Main__3low-c3b50454.jpg
